  m_text: 'The 1000-THR "Earthmover", also known as Benjamin by the ULTRAKILL Community,
    is a Supreme Machine and the boss fought at the climax of the Violence layer,
    [ 7-4: ...LIKE ANTENNAS TO HEAVEN ]. Earthmovers are visible throughout most
    of the Violence layer, with three Earthmovers visible in the distance in [ 7-2:
    LIGHT UP THE NIGHT ] and a lone Earthmover looming over the forests of [ 7-3:
    NO SOUND, NO MEMORY ].'
